    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a brand new home! It\u2019s been a fantastic companion and is in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a reliable car for daily commutes or fun weekend trips. It runs smoothly and has been well-cared for over the years. You're going to love how it feels on the road\u2014come take it for a test drive and see for yourself!",
