    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp throttle response and an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain delivers power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis has been meticulously maintained with an emphasis on structural integrity, including reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and uprated bushings. Braking performance remains consistent under load thanks to vented rotors and braided stainless steel lines. A mechanically robust example that prioritizes kinematic precision and tactile feedback.",
